body.p: The following Scandinavians bought or sold real estate in Chicago recently:
Gustaf Olson to Carl J. Johnson: Foster Avenue and Paulina Street. Price, $2,347.
Carl Hendriksen to Arthur C. P. Miller: Byron Street and Lavergne Avenue. Price, $1.
William Sievert to Herman P. Sievert: Armitage and Hamlin Avenues. Price, $1.
Elmer E. Bye to Frank Christman: Albany and Waveland Avenues. Price, $4,500.
D. N. Hansen to R. D. Vaughn: Marmora and Belden Avenues. Price, $10.
William S. Young to Marine K. Jepson: Newcastle Avenue and Altgeld Street. Price, $2,150.
H. P. Nelson to Fort Dearborn Trust and Savings Bank: Chicago and Spaulding Avenues. Price, $200,000.
Reynert Renertson to William Jude: Upton Street and Western Avenue. Price, $10.
Albert Henriksen to Thomas Pasek: Cicero, lot 6, blocks 5, 20, 39 and 13. Price, $1,000.
Johanne C. Larsen to Louis Sedlak: Cicero, 22nd Street Boulevard Subdivision, lots 1-4, blocks 8, 29, 29 and 13. Price, $10.

Hilda . Berg to Bertha Kuhe: Schumacher Subdivision, Leyden, lots 38 and 39,
block 23. Price, $1.
Carl Johann Frederick Petersen to Frank Pil: Fullerton and Narragansett Avenues, ten acres. Price, $50,000.
